verses.text: \w The|strong="H3117"\w* Lord hath reigned, \w he|strong="H3117"\w* \w is|strong="H3117"\w* clothed \w with|strong="H3117"\w* beauty: \w the|strong="H3117"\w* Lord \w is|strong="H3117"\w* clothed \w with|strong="H3117"\w* strength, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* hath girded \w himself|strong="H3117"\w*. \w For|strong="H3117"\w* \w he|strong="H3117"\w* hath established \w the|strong="H3117"\w* world which \w shall|strong="H3117"\w* not \w be|strong="H3117"\w* moved.
Thy throne \w is|strong="H3068"\w* prepared \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* old: thou art \w from|strong="H3068"\w* everlasting.

\w The|strong="H5046"\w* floods have lifted \w up|strong="H3915"\w*, O \w Lord|strong="H2617"\w*: \w the|strong="H5046"\w* floods have lifted \w up|strong="H3915"\w* \w their|strong="H5046"\w* voice. \w The|strong="H5046"\w* floods have lifted \w up|strong="H3915"\w* \w their|strong="H5046"\w* waves,

\w With|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* noise \w of|strong="H5921"\w* many waters. Wonderful are \w the|strong="H5921"\w* surges \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* sea: wonderful is \w the|strong="H5921"\w* Lord \w on|strong="H5921"\w* high.
Thy testimonies \w are|strong="H3027"\w* become exceedingly credible: holiness becometh thy house, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*, unto length \w of|strong="H3068"\w* days.
